<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb81e6679-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea" identifier="/us/usc/t5/s3385"><num value="3385">§ 3385.</num><heading> Effect on other authority</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">This subchapter shall not limit the authority of the Secretary to reassign temporarily an air traffic controller to other duties with or without notice, in the interest of the safe or efficient separation and control of air traffic or the physical or mental health of a controller; or to reassign permanently or separate a controller under any other provision of law.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb81e667a-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/92/297/s3/a">Pub. L. 92–297, § 3(a)</ref>, <date date="1972-05-16">May 16, 1972</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/86/143">86 Stat. 143</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/96/347/s1/b">Pub. L. 96–347, § 1(b)</ref>, <date date="1980-09-12">Sept. 12, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/1150">94 Stat. 1150</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idb81e667b-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idb81e667c-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I75" topic="referencesInText" id="idb81e667d-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">References in Text</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">For definition of Secretary, referred to in text, see <ref href="/us/usc/t5/s2109">section 2109 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idb81e667e-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1980—<ref href="/us/pl/96/347">Pub. L. 96–347</ref> substituted “Secretary” for “Secretary of Transportation”.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idb81e667f-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
