</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idb81e6681-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective on 90th day after <date date="1972-05-16">May 16, 1972</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/92/297/s10">section 10 of Pub. L. 92–297</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t5/s3381">section 3381 of this title</ref>.</p>
